era.it/tag/roberto-venturi/" rel="tag">Roberto Venturi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/saverio-marconi/" rel="tag">Saverio Marconi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/stefania-abbondi/" rel="tag">Stefania Abbondi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-massimo-palermo/" rel="tag">Teatro Massimo Palermo</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alessandro Camera, Anna Pirozzi, Annalisa Stroppa, Gaston Rivero, George Gagnidze, Giuseppe Verdi, Luiz-Ottavio Faria, Manrico Signorini, Mario Bolognesi, Nabucco, Orchestra del Teatro Massimo, Palermo, Piero Monti, Renato Palumbo, Roberto Venturi, Saverio Marconi, Stefania Abbondi, Teatro Massimo Palermo"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/f56370b7da5e03bbc648642da149afc1" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/100_1873-140x200.jpg" width="70" height="100" alt="Ilaria Grippaudo" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Ilaria Grippaudo"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/ilaria-grippaudo/">View all articles by Ilaria Grippaudo</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/03/napoli-teatro-di-san-carlo-don-chisciotte/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Napoli, Teatro di San Carlo, Don Chisciotte<